{"tid":1458482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔認同要怪散水撚","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:47:59.000Z","uid":277687,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b9b49d55df3a55a1de41f016d6349ab5e01ec4","tid":1458482,"uid":277687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"今日機場係有好多fake news<br />\n不過fact check都需要時間<br />\n今次係fake news<br />\n所以會怪人叫人散水<br />\n但如果嗰啲news係真<br />\n咁真係死好多人<br />\n<br />\n叫人走係因為擔心留喺度嘅人<br />\n真心唔想見到其他人受傷或被捕<br />\n決定唔走嘅人哋點逼都唔會走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要怪就要怪散播白色恐怖嘅人！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋亦想見到我哋怪嚟怪去<br />\n呢個係長期戰<br />\n每次行動目的係咩<br />\n一定要認清<br />\n留得越耐危險越大<br />\n<br />\n而家班狗唔係人<br />\n咩都做得出<br />\n今次走咗唔係輸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係我哋永遠都趕唔走<br />\n只要我哋永遠提住721 811</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0441cade8d17b9e6b5d04959167e858174a46d26","tid":1458482,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日機場係有好多fake news<br />\n不過fact check都需要時間<br />\n今次係fake news<br />\n所以會怪人叫人散水<br />\n但如果嗰啲news係真<br />\n咁真係死好多人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">叫人走係因為擔心留喺度嘅人<br />\n真心唔想見到其他人受傷或被捕<br />\n決定唔走嘅人哋點逼都唔會走</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要怪就要怪散播白色恐怖嘅人！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋亦想見到我哋怪嚟怪去<br />\n呢個係長期戰<br />\n每次行動目的係咩<br /